item.title: Spring Chasin’
item.description:
We think people who aren’t into golf don’t necessarily understand the grueling nature of a Member-Guest tournament. To make the shoot out is one goal, but to win it all ties in luck and straight puke-driven guts. That’s what happened to Mr. Pepe and Mr. Katzeff in the recent Pelican Golf Club Member-Guest. We open up and give Pep a big congrats and hear the story from him.

We revisit the recent Pine Needles Invitational that took place a few weeks ago with none of us making the cut.... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/chasin-birdies/
